latestIgtvVideos.title: How to use our Calligraphy Guideline Maker
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Drawing guidelines for Calligraphy was never this easy!! This life-changing Calligraphy Guideline Maker is our best-selling product and is designed to draw guidelines of different sizes, ratios and x-heights. It can aid in making wide guidelines so as to write on an A4 size paper. One edge of the stencil is at a slant of 55 degrees as required for Copperplate Calligraphy & can be used for other Modern Calligraphy Scripts. This video shows 5 different ways to use it, but there are many ways one can alter the guidelines according to their requirement.

Available to shop at www.stuscripts.com. Link in bio!!!
